// MessageArea (chat-drawer)
// Renders the chat message list, including artifact link notifications and inline AI UI components.
// Each message may contain artifact data (documents/diagrams) or structured AI UI components.

FUNCTION hasArtifactData(message) -> boolean
  Returns true if the message contains embedded artifact metadata.

---

FUNCTION getArtifactData(message) -> ArtifactData
  Extracts artifact name, type, and ID from the message payload.

---

FUNCTION handleArtifactClick(artifact)
  Opens the artifact in the viewer via viewerStore.

---

FUNCTION MessageArea(props) -> ReactNode                                  EXPORT
  CALLS: AIUIRenderer (renderer), ArtifactLink (ArtifactLink), useViewerStore (viewerStore)
  Renders each message in the list.
  IF the message has artifact data, renders an ArtifactLink below the message text.
  IF the message has AI UI components, renders them via AIUIRenderer.
  Scrolls to the bottom when new messages arrive.
